Gabriel's Dot Files

Modified from Faun's Dot Files
Credit to Ben Orenstein & Ryan Bates

These are config files to set up a system the way I like it.

Installation

  mkdir -p ~/src
  git clone --recursive git@github.com:ggilder/dotfiles ~/src/dotfiles
  cd ~/src/dotfiles
  rake install

